Name: Kao
Description: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes.
Progression: Rune, Basic, Lesser, Greater, Epic
Basic Rune: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes. Requires a Movement speed greater than or equal to DISTANCE20-30DISTANCE feet to attune.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACESPACECurse of SpeedSPACEAs an action, you attempt to curse a target within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be forced to take the Dash action on their next TIME1-2TIME turns, expending all of their available movement if possible. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 1 runic attunement slot. 
